divs: Sighting DetailsI have seen hundreds of these over last forty years and and most were like the last one which i got a vidieo of. Ther have been many other people in the area that have seen them over the years. This one was really not special just like most i have seen. I had just stepped out side and like to look for meteors and other night happenings, as i left my front porch i happened to see the light coming from the NWi went back inside and got my camera to take phots and also got about a minute of vidieo. I new at once what it was since i have seen them for years. The object flew straight over my house and in a straight line. No special reactions since i am familiar with these objects. I took vidieo until the object went behind trees.
Summary: Have hundreds over last forty years this is the lastest. Some as large as town others completly dark blocking out stars
